snippet.title: One Button Travel - Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon: One Button Travel is a new interactive fiction game by TheCodingMonkeys feat. Marcel-André Casasola Merkle  and Agnes Lison, the award-winning team behind Rules!. Are you ready to solve mysteries, explore a strange new world and meet horned beasts? Pack your bags, you're going on a trip! Or are you?

http://onebuttontravel.com
